    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, scratches, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls, and it still retains that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade example that needs nothing but a new home.",
