      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-preserved condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every aspect of this specimen\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its meticulously maintained mechanical components\u2014reflects an uncompromising standard of care. This is an investment-grade motorcar for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
