    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every maintenance schedule. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a superlative E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully overhauled for optimal phase timing. This specimen features a structurally reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure\u2014and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains as rigid as the day it left Regensburg. The paint depth is consistent across all panels with zero signs of oxidation or clear coat failure, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
